  <releases>
    <release version="26.4.3" date="2026-04-21">
      <description>
        <p>Performance and polish pass, focused on Linux phones like the Librem 5. The app starts and switches views noticeably faster on lower-end ARM hardware, and the consequential-action buttons now carry the standard red tint.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Cold start is roughly twice as fast on slow ARM phones; view switches, session start, and session end no longer stall the UI</li>
          <li>Haptic feedback on session end now fires correctly on devices with feedbackd, without the end-sound doubling up</li>
          <li>Stop, Discard, and per-session delete buttons are styled as destructive (red) per the GNOME HIG</li>
          <li>Log view loads 15 sessions per page by default instead of 200, with Load more for older entries</li>
        </ul>
      </description>
    </release>

    <release version="26.4.2" date="2026-04-21">
      <description>
        <p>Major polish release ahead of Flathub submission — every tab redesigned, new data features, and translations in nine languages.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Timer, Stats, and Log tabs fully redesigned around the GNOME HIG</li>
          <li>Stats now shows a weekly-goal ring, a 13-week contribution heatmap, and an insights panel</li>
          <li>Log is a date-grouped card feed with swipe-to-delete and undo</li>
          <li>CSV import and export, plus one-click migration from Insight Timer</li>
          <li>Real CC0 recordings replace the three built-in end sounds, with Singing bowl as the new default</li>
          <li>Post-session note field is now multi-line</li>
          <li>Weekly goal resets on the locale's first day of the week</li>
          <li>New "Vibrate on session end" toggle for Linux phones</li>
          <li>Full translation coverage across English, German, Spanish, French, Italian, Dutch, Polish, Brazilian Portuguese, Russian, and Simplified Chinese</li>
          <li>Adaptive layout down to 360 px; HIG-compliant accent colours and accessibility</li>
        </ul>
      </description>
    </release>
    <release version="26.4.1" date="2026-04-13">
      <description>
        <p>Initial release.</p>
      </description>
    </release>
  </releases>

  <supports>
    <control>pointing</control>
    <control>keyboard</control>
    <control>touch</control>
  </supports>

  <requires>
    <display_length compare="ge">360</display_length>
  </requires>
</component>
